1 (b) Offense. – A person commits the offense of larceny of gift cards if the person does
2 any of the following:
3 (1) Acquires or retains possession of a gift card or gift card redemption
4 information without the consent of the cardholder or card issuer.
5 (2) Obtains a gift card or gift card redemption information from a cardholder or
