9 another.
10 (c) Punishment. – A violation of this section is a Class 1 misdemeanor if the value of the
11 gift card acquired, retained, or for which the card redemption information is obtained, or is altered
12 or tampered with, is not more than one thousand dollars ($1,000). Any other violation of this
13 section is a Class H felony."
